<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>FAQs</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('sidebar.ejs') %>

    <div class="content">
        <h1>🧐 Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
        <hr>

        <div class="faq-grid">
            <!-- Essay-Related FAQs -->
            <div class="faq-box">
                <h3>📌 What is the main theme of "How to WikiHow"?</h3>
                <p>Explore the main theme and key points of the essay "How to WikiHow."</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-box">
                <h3>📌 Discuss the content of the essay titled "Exploring JavaScript."</h3>
                <p>Provide an overview and analysis of the content in the essay about JavaScript.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-box">
                <h3>📌 What ethical considerations are discussed in "Artificial Intelligence and Ethics"?</h3>
                <p>Examine the ethical considerations highlighted in the essay on Artificial Intelligence and Ethics.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-box">
                <h3>📌 Explore the impact of climate change as discussed in "The Impact of Climate Change."</h3>
                <p>Summarize the environmental, social, and economic impacts explored in the essay.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-box">
                <h3>📌 How does the essay "Space Exploration: Past, Present, and Future" cover humanity's journey into space?</h3>
                <p>Discuss the comprehensive look at space exploration and the prospects for the future.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Site-Related FAQs -->
            <div class="faq-box">
                <h3>🌍 What is this site about?</h3>
                <p>This site is a collection of essays on various topics, ranging from technology to philosophy.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-box">
                <h3>📝 Can I contribute my own essays?</h3>
                <p>Yes! Click on "New Essay" in the sidebar to submit your own essay.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-box">
                <h3>🔍 How do I find an essay I'm interested in?</h3>
                <p>Use the "Essays" page to browse topics or use the search feature (coming soon!).</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-box">
                <h3>🛠️ Can I edit or delete my essays?</h3>
                <p>Yes! Click the "Edit" or "Delete" buttons next to your essay in the Essays section.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-box">
                <h3>📩 How can I contact you?</h3>
                <p>Visit the "Contact" page in the sidebar to send us a message.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
